snippet.title: Pit of Goblin - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The DEMO of Pit of Goblin is now LIVE!! An online horror co-op, where you play as a goblin, scavenging dungeons, and fleeing monsters to feed the Goblin King. 👑

Go play the demo now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3304790/Pit_of_Goblin_Demo/
